{"type": "article", "id": 17485, "title": "纸揉时钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-13T06:10:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155712ikwL0DJ4Wl8GnEYB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Veronika Szalai 做了这个可以自己 DIY 的时钟，它的“表盘”是一种棉纸，你可以在不影响指针的前提下任意揉搓，形成任何有立体感的图案。它没有秒针也没有刻度，仅用这种有些潇洒的态度来表达对时间的感觉。然而吊诡的是，无论怎样揉搓时间都依然存在，也许在这个过程里就缓解了来自时间的压力。<a href=\"http://veronikaszalai.com/2015/10/18/new-time/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144609AzQfgRbBail0XxSZ.gif\" width=\"788\" height=\"526\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66751269\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144612EaTzHv69JBNr4xqy.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144612ShdxC62zqrBRfb4w.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144613CBPpIs31rtfNkmQM.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144613L18rTUHOBtR39wmf.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144614Nd1RWXuweZSakl6C.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}